{"tid":2139524,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉企圖警署外縱火 失業會計師獲准取回15萬保釋金","createTime":"2020-08-04T10:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T06:00:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"0804e640046f4a492c35a2433821617aa8db660f","tid":2139524,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T10:45:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/T3CQRCCXQVUQRWL2MRCWTFLNZQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FT3CQRCCXQVUQRWL2MRCWTFLNZQ%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4YdwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=05e306b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FT3CQRCCXQVUQRWL2MRCWTFLNZQ%2F&h=61273a2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/T3CQRCCXQVUQRWL2MRCWTFLNZQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n區域法院今午處理多宗涉及反修例示威的提訊案件。中年男會計師涉於去年8月手持天拿水和報紙碎，企圖在元朗警署外縱火，被指警誡下曾經透露打算「嚇吓警察」。他被控企圖縱火罪，案件今於區院再訊。辯方申請將30萬保釋金減半，透露此案令被告失去工作出現財困。法官高勁修批准申請，同意將保釋金減至15萬，並押後案件至9月1日再訊。"},{"pid":"9c988dfc298ccd9cd2b31650e696625de36b34f4","tid":2139524,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T10:47:57.000Z","msg":"另一宗示威案件亦於同庭再訊，年輕地盤工人疑於理大攻防戰當日，於旺角向一輛警車投擲汽油彈，汽油彈未有擊中警車，地盤工被捕，並被搜出軍刀及萬用刀等物。<strong><span class=\"red\">他今表示將會承認蓄意縱火以及管有攻擊性武器罪</span></strong>，控方指將就其管有物品意圖損壞財產罪撤控。案件押後至11月20日進行答辯及求情，被告繼續還押候訊。<br />\n<br />\n去年 11 月 8 日，大批市民到將軍澳悼念墮樓後不治的科大生周梓樂，悼念及後演變為堵路示威，其間有人疑指示威者嘈吵，與現場人士起爭執，當場遭「私了」至血流披面。<strong><span class=\"red\">一男一女被控暴動及有意圖傷人兩罪，兩人還押至今已逾 8 個月。案件今日在西九龍裁判法院再訊，代表律師透露二人將承認所有控罪。</span></strong>兩被告將於 11 月 6 日在區域法院答辯及求情，兩人沒有保釋申請，須繼續還押。"},{"pid":"f5f401b276c9e05b14cdb46a41bbe38a72655db2","tid":2139524,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T10:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abf590d3cb4109be7069fe9922a9a221edd5250","tid":2139524,"uid":132587,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06cd5f0687a0acda99fd31c3b8ebfd54dfc543db","tid":2139524,"uid":202425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6abf590d3cb4109be7069fe9922a9a221edd5250","tid":2139524,"uid":132587,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d85b6f871821aa3eda7333a10f0b416d2ea3aa","tid":2139524,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T10:53:33.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb10605596a0100ee9b0a3c59d483197240e8e87","tid":2139524,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T10:54:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7408d28472a42ebf086d6c99b9ccf3278646bbf7","tid":2139524,"uid":180168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T10:58:30.000Z","msg":"佢好夠膽<br />\n做會計師都肯出去"},{"pid":"fd4bc3687e234b7620d75468656a75fa04c981e2","tid":2139524,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T10:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3053667f0448fc34b33b9ff16926d4a05282560e","tid":2139524,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6abf590d3cb4109be7069fe9922a9a221edd5250","tid":2139524,"uid":132587,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime